255
00:15:42,477 --> 00:15:45,520
Now, of course,
the 100 mL test should have

256
00:15:45,520 --> 00:15:49,339
about 100 times as many bacteria
as the 1 mL test,

257
00:15:49,339 --> 00:15:52,921
so if that ratio is very different,
