300
00:18:19,562 --> 00:18:21,735
or for monitoring an intervention,

301
00:18:21,735 --> 00:18:24,425
like a household
water treatment intervention,

302
00:18:24,425 --> 00:18:28,384
even a limited amount of microbial testing
